        h2 Picker Events
        p Picker has the same events as any <a href="modal.html">Modal</a>
        table.events-table
          thead
            tr
              th Event
              th Target
              th Description
          tbody
            tr
              td open
              td Picker Element<span>&lt;div class="picker-modal"&gt;</span>
              td Event will be triggered when Picker starts its opening animation
            tr
              td opened
              td Picker Element<span>&lt;div class="picker-modal"&gt;</span>
              td Event will be triggered after Picker completes its opening animation
            tr
              td close
